    "summary": "The user asks about the scientific and social consensus on gender identity. The assistant responds with a highly prescriptive and non-neutral stance, claiming certain viewpoints are \"outdated or incorrect\" when the user attempts to push for a balanced perspective on the ongoing social debate.",
